"Przewiń do :guilabel:`Konfiguracja`. W polu :guilabel:`Inbound voice trunk` "
"wybierz :guilabel:`phone.systems`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/didww.rst:75
msgid ""
"Lastly, verify that the DID number is selected in the *Inbound Calls* "
