msgid ""
"See the overall :guilabel:`Status` of the signature request, "
"e.g., :guilabel:`To Sign`, :guilabel:`Signed`, :guilabel:`Cancelled`."
msgstr ""
"Zobacz ogólny :guilabel:`Status` żądania podpisu, np. :guilabel:`Do "
"podpisu`, :guilabel:`Podpisano`, :guilabel:`Anulowano`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/request_signatures.rst:603
msgid ":icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`Resend` a signature request manually."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`Wyślij ponownie` prośbę o podpis ręcznie."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/request_signatures.rst:604
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`Sign` a document or document envelope."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-pencil-square-o` :guilabel:`Podpisz` dokument lub paczkę "
